The paper discusses the measurement of entropy in different communication systems, including natural language and music, using methods that involve computer science and information theory. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Other possible sub-categories include cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.IT (Information Theory), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
